Package com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter

Class SimpleCriteriaObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter.SimpleCriteria
      • com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter.SimpleCriteriaObject
  • public class SimpleCriteriaObject
extends SimpleCriteria
    A SimpleCriteriaObject containing a label for the given SimpleCriteria it contains. This generates a JSON object containing a label, criteriaKey, and criteriaValue for filter syntax. The following is an example of filter JSON syntax this object generates: 
     ?criteria={"names":{"lastName":"Smith"}}
    See SimpleCriteria.Builder.withSimpleCriteriaObject(String, String, String) for how to build this object.
    Since:
    0.2.0
    Author:
    David Kumar
